'''Ronald Gordon Giovanelli''' DSc [[Fellow of the Australian Academy of Science|FAA]] (1915&ndash;1984) was an Australian physicist and solar researcher. <ref name=ADB>{{cite web |author= W.R. Blevin |title= Giovanelli, Ronald Gordon (1915–1984) |publisher= Australian Dictionary of Biography, National Centre of Biography, Australian National University |url= http://adb.anu.edu.au/biography/giovanelli-ronald-gordon-12543 }} first published in Australian Dictionary of Biography, Volume 17, (MUP), 2007.</ref><ref name=AAS>{{cite web |author= J.H. Piddington |title= Ronald Gordon Giovanelli 1915–1984 |work= Biographical Memoirs of Deceased Fellows |publisher= Australian Academy of Science |url= http://www.asap.unimelb.edu.au/bsparcs/aasmemoirs/giovanel.htm }} originally published in ''Historical Records of Australian Science'', vol 6, no 2, 1985, p 223. </ref><ref name=trove>[http://trove.nla.gov.au/people/629439?c=people Giovanelli, R. G. (Ronald Gordon) (1915–1984)], trove.nla.gov.au</ref><ref name=eoas>[http://www.eoas.info/biogs/P000440b.htm Giovanelli, Ronald Gordon (1915–1984)], Encyclopaedia of Australian Science</ref><ref name=ASAObit>{{cite journal |author= K.V. Sheridan |title= Obituary - Giovanelli, Ron |journal= Proceedings of the Astronomical Society of Australia |volume=6 |number=1 |pages=112-113 |date= 1985 |url= http://adsabs.harvard.edu/full/1985PASAu...6..112S }} </ref> 

